        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         These guys are circling a pool in the very NorthEast corner of the zone.</P><P>So far I have gotten some meteor dust, that shard for the vex thal key (I think) and some blocks of that crap you need for seru bane weapons.  Dunno what else they can drop.</P><P>You probably want shadowbond and pact of shadow both up.  Shadowbond should be good enough 80% of the time but they have a tendancy of getting on a lucky streak that requires pact to back it up.  Also, you need to re-shackle part way through because these are not the shortest fights in the world if you want to save enough mana to kill a few of these.  Also, as soon as your pet gets on the thing, feign.  The slow will aggro you enough that it'll take a good while to get the thing off you otherwise.</P><P>I am sure that a steady stream of dark blue tormented Iksar slaves would be faster exp but finding a steady stream of them just isn't going to happen.  You're gunna get light blues and set off traps and get shimmering cockfiends on ya and it's just a pain in the ass compared to this, imo.</P><P><A href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=26159">Reegor</A> Mortees<BR>scaled Warlock<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
